body:
For certain charts like Pie chart, Row chart, and possibly others, when you choose "# Records" as your size measure, it would often be useful to see a % of records value, instead of # records value.

Perhaps we could have a toggle below (like we do for avg/min/max,etc.) which would have 2 settings, one for Count the other for Percentage.

@tmostak

